properties.description: Posted by Jorgensenmusic 216 State St Madison, WI 53703-2215Tag, the promoter of my glorious homecoming show, once yelled at me on State Street because I was flyering for a Magic City show and using masking tape. "At least be professional," he said. In my whole time in Madison, I never attended a show at the stage door, and now I know why.

properties.name: club Deville
properties.description: Posted by Jorgensenmusic 900 Red River St, Austin, TXAfter the show, we saw a tourist randomly get punched in the face by a local kid. He was hurt really bad. A cop was right there, but didn\'t bother to do anything and asked the victim if he felt like chasing the aggressor. If he had wanted to, the cop would have had to arrest him. That was when we knew it was time to leave Austin.
